How to reset User Password ?

1. Identify the User Name from case description
Steps Perform on User OBject
2. Check the user is exist or not, If not exist then send email to customer that user doesn't exist
3. If Exist check user is active or not at user object
4. If not active , Activate user then send reset password
5. Finally send an email to customer to chekc the issue has been resolved or not
